narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: we just used desk space. It might be nice to have parallel rules available. I don't imagine using the one I had to put together just for this class.

I mostly used the DMCA to print. The printers at YSOA are too broken/abused, and too many people wear them out, to do art-quality printing for digital work. But they are OK for everyday test printing.
